Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.80,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}衝口而出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.68,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}流露而出的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.22,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}現在 悄悄 定是
