Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.85,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}迴轉不息的夢境之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.15,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}與你一度一度反覆起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:21.53,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}搖曳的景色 旅途在繼續
