Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,-----------------ED-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:05.22,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這全都是你親手做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:07.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 從採購到成品都是我一手包辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請品嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是讓我見識一下你工作的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 如你所見 我這是絕讚工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你是小說家來著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那麼多 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我將其命名為「春妖精的全裸湯」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:27.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.97,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:13.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是職業作家 這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:18.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為喜歡的人親手下廚的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我充分理解女主角為別人做料理的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.08,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我是把寫小說當作遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:31.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不認真玩的話豈不是太無聊了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為是遊戲才要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,託你的福 我可能更喜歡下廚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:52.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧 這是鄰居讓我帶給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,鄰居親手做的料理 很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:04.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.94,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz13.96\pos(656,800)\c&H7E7277&}鄰居？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,eromanga 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.96\pos(772,836)\c&H7E7277&}關係一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:11.82,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:13.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.03,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真色情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢 還有其他要說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:25.37,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 為什麼你只會畫貧乳的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我要求你把女主角的胸部畫大一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.39,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會無視掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.26,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我對色色的畫有自己的講究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想畫那些自己沒有親眼見過的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.33,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,親…親眼是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那張插畫難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太下流了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:03:59.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 好色 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.80,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛絕對想像了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,用我來想像十分色情的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定覺得我是為了畫出那麼色情的插畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.86,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才買那種細繩內褲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後覺得我很色情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒那麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有想到那種程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.69,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是不會用妹妹來想色情的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:26.97,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你多麼色情 都不會對你有色慾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.62,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況 絕對不會瞧不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,像笨蛋似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.25,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這種即好色又說謊的哥哥我才不認識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.26,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個莫非是妖…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.24,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁的山田小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.65,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H7B6B71&\frz33.3\pos(798,894)}鄰居？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.65,eromanga 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H7B6B71&\pos(904,904)\frz27.53}關係一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,鄰居？關係一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.15,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz36\pos(1658.666,402.667)\c&H7D767D&}呀吼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.91,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呀吼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.11,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz26.43\c&H6A5D63&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(594,422)}鄰居親手做的料理非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,鄰居親手做的料理非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.40,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:13.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我最近經常去隔壁 但那是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:13.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,總是這樣 不管什麼都謊話連篇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥什麼的 最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想看到你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:33.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要證明我不是騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我這一年裡面一直都在考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才能讓你認可我是你真正的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.41,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事情我現在清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧 我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓妹妹當女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:49.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我要寫以妹妹為題材的輕小說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我要寫自己最喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後創作出究極的輕小說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點都不開心 不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.59,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做才不會讓我打開心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只會讓我感到噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.73,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,滿嘴謊言的哥哥我最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.53,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.98,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:34.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 幹勁全開地做我能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.21,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,過了幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,轉眼間就也快半個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:54.66,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後我就再也沒有跟紗霧見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:07:00.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 新作的企劃請無論如何也要在這個星期交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,請稍微給我一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:08.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚了 那麼請你慢慢思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕工作是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.88,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不出新作的話 我的一席之地就會馬上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.25,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至會被粉絲忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼寫都出版不了一本書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話一下子就會回到滿受挫折的前年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,即使要和這樣的恐懼進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫出了有趣的東西 也很有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.82,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,門是開著的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.29,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山田妖精老師 不在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.21,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那我擅自進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.03,eromanga 6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,508)\fs60\c&H735961&\b1}月境辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,妖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.62,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 話說今天是約定的日子來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,請在客廳等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.52,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.98,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次看見她那麼認真的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.21,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的新作小說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天不是一個字都還沒寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力「完成原稿召喚」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1081.6,1004.8)}Summon Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,把完成原稿從魔界召喚出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼可能 居然有這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.48,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為這樣能嚇得到我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在超拚命地趕稿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.66,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒寫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我從魔界召喚出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是覺得我說謊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就調查一下我的筆記本電腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你刪掉了嗎 就為了這種無聊的小戲法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山…山田妖精的新作…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:00.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山田妖精就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:05.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看 原稿不就在這裡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一決勝負吧 和泉征宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就用我的「神眼」看穿你的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(900.8,1003.2)}God Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.41,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意 山田妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:16.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我來讀一讀你這從魔界召喚出來的全力以赴的小說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣 非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,手和心越讀越停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是動畫化作家的實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.37,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這部作品 女主角全都是貧乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,儘是埃羅芒阿老師擅長的姿勢 喜歡的場景和服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 總而言之就是很色情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完全特化到了極限
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是為埃羅芒阿老師量身定做的輕小說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你這份…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你這份原稿 是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:00.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.53,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是還是不是啊 征宗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點很重要 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.45,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是很認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 根本贏不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我的原稿有這麼有趣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.45,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 我才沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你居然敢給我看這種東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的 這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:48.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫的作品肯定比你的好賣百億倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.91,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.53,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不就不能好好一決勝負了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.46,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:11:01.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這份原稿根本不是為了讓很多讀者開心而寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:08.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你往這裡邊注入了靈魂 只為了某個人而寫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:12.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讀完這份不能作為商品的垃圾原稿之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.70,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感情會被動搖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:19.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個世界上就只有我和你的妹妹 埃羅芒阿老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.59,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讀完以後當然會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.41,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:31.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這就像是寫著「埃羅芒阿老師是你的妹妹」一樣明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:36.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想讓我的妹妹讀一讀這份作品的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:38.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.91,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法肯定會好好傳達到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:46.77,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這份足足有三百頁的超超超熱烈情書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,本來還以為你的暴露癖是有多嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:56.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你卻居然毫無自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 輸了輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.88,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你…這是幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:06.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:10.08,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼色情且有趣的傑作被永遠地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是感謝你的誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算留下來也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有她畫的插畫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:18.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有言在先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.50,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是我輸了 而不是你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.02,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這有什麼不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才說你遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.82,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來原稿你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會說出「不打算讓妹妹看了」這種話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給就給 我原本就這麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.73,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.48,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是掉下去可就不僅僅是受傷那麼簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.25,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,埃羅芒阿老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.03,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧 我現在就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:28.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是…那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧 新作的原稿寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:32.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你讀讀看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 雖然你的做法很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做那麼危險的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為從那以後你一直都閉門不開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.59,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.43,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一段時間閉門不開的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥場面 畫得好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.55,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,與之前相比簡直天差地別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.02,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看了格鬥技的比賽視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也看了很多武器的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才畫得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:16.83,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我並不太喜歡死人或者受傷的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:22.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我就說過了 不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.52,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我對喜歡的角色逝去感到很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以至今為止都有所牴觸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:32.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是第一次和你面對面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,交談創作的話題的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:38.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我便覺得只把自己喜歡的東西畫得好是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我說你畫很爛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我覺得也必須戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.62,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥？是跟我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 也看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,上色之後就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊的是不同髮型的版本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.02,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 連巨乳角色都能駕馭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是畫出能讓人看的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,脫掉之後就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,超色情 超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 這半個月她都在練習這些東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和泉老師 這樣就清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓我負責你的新作是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？ 那是什麼 誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:33.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你有事情瞞著我 還和隔壁的山田小姐悄悄碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來還很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥不會在工作以外的地方認識那種女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.35,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,自從你遇見她以後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你就變得十分有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:49.46,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人肯定是新的插畫師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就一直關起房門來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:53.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:16:00.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和泉老師讓妹妹成為主角 然後創作出究極的輕小說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.18,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實是非常開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.83,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想著肯定得讓我來畫插畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.88,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對絕對不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會把和泉老師讓給那種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話該由我說才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:20.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:25.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁的山田小姐是人氣作家山田妖精老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山田妖精老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:32.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對 那傢伙…那傢伙是埃羅芒阿老師的大粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.80,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,她想和你一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:39.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我賭上了埃羅芒阿老師 跟她進行了小說對決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊 我聽都沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.40,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:50.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你可能會說「與其和我一起 更想和人氣作家一起工作」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.63,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 哥哥真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,連我自己也是這麼覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:01.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為最後還是得不得不說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的 那個方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:10.77,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 但是我已經解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 居然贏了她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和泉老師好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:23.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然原本是想讓你讀完再做決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初就是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始也請多指教了 和泉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.98,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是呢 請多指教 埃羅芒阿老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不認識叫那種名字的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在慌什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.66,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 才沒有慌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有 一點都沒有慌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.50,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就過去對面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:29.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 緊張得快要休剋死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.68,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.09,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:40.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 我覺得十分有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:41.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:46.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 就這樣出書是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:51.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能讓別人看 太羞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:19:02.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:09.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:15.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是兄妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定要當她的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.18,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 這樣啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 笑成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.50,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 接下來怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:12.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 紗霧 我也有夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:12.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 非常大的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:19.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓這份原稿出書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.69,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不能就這樣直接出書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.63,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我重新進行構思 寫出企劃書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後讓責編認可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.69,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然要從這一步開始 但是肯定會出成書的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:35.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓很多的人感到有趣並且喜歡上男女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後人氣不斷攀升
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:39.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,並且賺得可以輕鬆生活的費用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.03,eromanga 3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\b1\fs40\c&H6570DF&\frz29.49\pos(273.6,176)}祝賀動畫化!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.03,eromanga 3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HE0B12D&\frz30\fs40\pos(345.6,292.8)}和泉先生的簽名會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再接著就是動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.48,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是哥哥的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:47.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不對不對 那些都是準備而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是給我們的客廳買上一個大的液晶電視
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再準備一個超貴的音響
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在豪華的蛋糕上面點上蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,把你從房間裡面帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:58.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起看動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,由我負責原作 你負責插畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:03.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:07.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 我覺得肯定會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷的事情可能會被一掃而空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:12.86,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我絕對要實現的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:22.39,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喊得聲音太大有點喘不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:26.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 這次也是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紗霧 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:46.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你從以前就是這樣呢 和泉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:51.80,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,總是都能給予我夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:55.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 和泉老師 來大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:59.57,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼有趣的事情怎麼可以讓你獨占呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那不僅僅是你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它成為我們一起的夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.03,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:16.52,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:21.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,向著夢想踏出的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:27.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概一生都不會忘記這天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:33.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 和妹妹一起制定輕小說企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,eromanga 5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs80\fn@萝莉体 第二版\pos(1726,332)}哥哥...
